<!-- Banner -->
<div class="banner-peetayers" style="background-image: linear-gradient(-225deg, rgba(0,101,168,0.6) 0%, rgba(0,36,61,0.6) 50%), url('<%=image_path "https://source.unsplash.com/collection/865018/1000x300"%>');">
  <div class="banner-peetayers-content">
    <h1>Welcome</h1>
  </div>
</div>
<!-- End Banner -->

<div class="container">
  <div class="body">
    <div class="row">

      <div class="column-1">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-3">
          <div class="polaroid flo">
            <div class="polaroid-img" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.2)), url('<%=image_path "peetayers/franco.jpg" %>');">
            </div>
            <p class="polaroid-text"><strong>Franco, 23 ans<strong></p>
            <p class="polaroid-desc">"I would like to share local tips"</p>
          </div>
          <br>

          <div class="infos">
            <div class="infos-title text-center">
              <p><strong>Information checked</strong></p>
            </div>
            <div class="infos-content">
              <ul><p><i class="far fa-check-circle"></i> Official ID</p></ul>
              <ul><p><i class="far fa-check-circle"></i> Phone</p></ul>
              <ul><p><i class="far fa-check-circle"></i> Email</p></ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="column-2">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-9">

            <div class="row">
              <div class="space1 text-center">
                <div class="space1-title">
                  <h3>Hello, I'm Franco!</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="space1-content">
                  <p>Lille, France Â° for 4 years</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="space2">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                  <div class="space2-title">
                    <p><strong>Available services</strong></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                  <div class="space2-content">
                    <div class="row">
                      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                        <%= image_tag "flaticon/suitcase.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                        <p>Prepare your trip</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                        <%= image_tag "flaticon/location.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                        <p>Housing services</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                        <%= image_tag "flaticon/medical-history.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                        <p>Help with admins</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                        <%= image_tag "flaticon/chat.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                        <p>Speak local</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                        <%= image_tag "flaticon/cheers.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                        <p>Local tips</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                        <%= image_tag "flaticon/masks.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                        <p>Cultural outings</p>
                      </div>
                      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                        <%= image_tag "flaticon/football.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                        <p>Play sports</p>
                      <div class="col-xs-6 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
                        <%= image_tag "flaticon/welcome.png", class: "space2-photo" %>
                        <p>Be welcomed</p>
                      </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="space2">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                  <div class="space2-title">
                    <p><strong>Languages?</strong></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                  <div class="space2-content">
                    <p>French & English</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="space2">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                  <div class="space2-title">
                    <p><strong>Why do you like Lille?</strong></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                  <div class="space2-content">
                    <p>I really like Lille because it's a city on a human scale with very welcoming inhabitants, so, it's very easy to meet people.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="space2">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                  <div class="space2-title">
                    <p><strong>Your favorite spots in Lille?</strong></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                  <div class="space2-content">
                    <p>The Notre-Dame-de-la-Treille Cathedral, the park of "La Citadelle", the Saint-Sauveur train station.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="space2">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                  <div class="space2-title">
                    <p><strong>Why do you want to become a Peetayer?</strong></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                  <div class="space2-content">
                    <p>I want to become a Peetayer to discover my city, share my local tips and meet new people from a different culture.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="space2">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                  <div class="space2-title">
                    <p><strong>What are your interests?</strong></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                  <div class="space2-content">
                    <p>Outings with friens, everything about enterpreneurship, sports and music.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
              <div class="space2">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-md-4">
                  <div class="space2-title">
                    <p><strong>What about Franco?</strong></p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8">
                  <div class="space2-content">
                    <p>Franco has been a youngster from Lille for 5 years. Entrepreneur and sportsman, he likes to share moments with his friends during parties in the "Vieux Lille" (old town). He loves meeting people and sharing his good plans.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>

